{"tid":1599504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗9．21兩漢遭「私了」受傷　兩男涉傷人被捕","createTime":"2019-09-28T04:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T04:37:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc72985563f1004daaa7ef861ba0baf3eeb287e7","tid":1599504,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:26:18.000Z","msg":"元朗上周六（21日）深夜至周日（22日）凌晨發生多宗涉不同政見者衝突，兩名中年漢被示威者以「私了」形式襲擊，受傷送院。新界北總區重案組人員接手調查案件，昨日（27日）分別在深水埗麗安邨及元朗洪福邨拘捕一名25歲陳姓男子及一名30歲張姓男子，涉嫌傷人，二人將被通宵扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被襲傷者分別為52歲及38歲的本地男子，上周六深夜至周日凌晨疑在元朗大馬路被一批示威者以手腳、玻璃樽、棍及雨傘等襲擊，二人頭部受傷，清醒被送往博愛醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190928/s00001/1569638695866/%e5%85%83%e6%9c%979-21%e5%85%a9%e6%bc%a2%e9%81%ad%e3%80%8c%e7%a7%81%e4%ba%86%e3%80%8d%e5%8f%97%e5%82%b7-%e5%85%a9%e7%94%b7%e6%b6%89%e5%82%b7%e4%ba%ba%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190928%2Fs00001%2F1569638695866%2F%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%25979-21%25e5%2585%25a9%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e9%2581%25ad%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25a7%2581%25e4%25ba%2586%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%2582%25b7-%25e5%2585%25a9%25e7%2594%25b7%25e6%25b6%2589%25e5%2582%25b7%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=3dba8925\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190928%2Fs00001%2F1569638695866%2F%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%25979-21%25e5%2585%25a9%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e9%2581%25ad%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25a7%2581%25e4%25ba%2586%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%2582%25b7-%25e5%2585%25a9%25e7%2594%25b7%25e6%25b6%2589%25e5%2582%25b7%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595&h=b5063f4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190928/s00001/1569638695866/%e5%85%83%e6%9c%979-21%e5%85%a9%e6%bc%a2